    <content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Add the following config in the front matter of your post to get a stunning edge to edge banner picture(hero).&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;figure class=&quot;highlight asciidoc&quot;&gt;&lt;table&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td class=&quot;gutter&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;2&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;3&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;4&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;5&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;6&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;7&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;8&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;9&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;10&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td class=&quot;code&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;bullet&quot;&gt;---&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;title: Test post&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;date: 2016-02-23&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;updated: 2016-02-29&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;hero:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;code&quot;&gt;  image: http://7fva40.com1.z0.glb.clouddn.com/carlog-404-sprite.jpg&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;code&quot;&gt;  size: cover&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;code&quot;&gt;  position: center&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;header&quot;&gt;  height: 450px&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;---&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This will add inline style to the &lt;code&gt;&amp;lt;header&amp;gt;&lt;/code&gt; element, rule mapping as below:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;figure class=&quot;highlight lisp&quot;&gt;&lt;table&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td class=&quot;gutter&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;2&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;3&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;4&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td class=&quot;code&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;* image    -&amp;gt; background-image    &lt;span class=&quot;list&quot;&gt;(&lt;span class=&quot;keyword&quot;&gt;this&lt;/span&gt; value can&lt;span class=&quot;quoted&quot;&gt;&#39;t&lt;/span&gt; be ommited)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;* size     -&amp;gt; background-size     &lt;span class=&quot;list&quot;&gt;(&lt;span class=&quot;keyword&quot;&gt;default&lt;/span&gt; to &lt;span class=&quot;string&quot;&gt;&quot;cover&quot;&lt;/span&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;* position -&amp;gt; background-position &lt;span class=&quot;list&quot;&gt;(&lt;span class=&quot;keyword&quot;&gt;default&lt;/span&gt; to &lt;span class=&quot;string&quot;&gt;&quot;center&quot;&lt;/span&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;* height   -&amp;gt; height              &lt;span class=&quot;list&quot;&gt;(&lt;span class=&quot;keyword&quot;&gt;default&lt;/span&gt; to &lt;span class=&quot;string&quot;&gt;&quot;450px&quot;&lt;/span&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;
